ygData.messageBody:
Oh I won't be there to pull. I will let the SK (52) or Shaman (53) handle that .
I am only there to Track/Manabattery/misc stuff. Nothing that shoudl agro me to
badly with the SK/Shaman/SHaman pet all going to town.. :-)

Of course Selo's will be mem'ed and MM Drum handy (both of the others have SOW
boots in one form or another).

I imagine we will hang near the EJ zone and kill roamers. And move in further if
we have to.

-Ranian

Wandering mobs are quite annoying. At level 35, be ready to pickup a
considerable number of creatures while you are pulling...most of the
creatures in the zone started "greening" for me around lvl 53..so that would
put alot of them close to your level range. The forager and hunter
themselves are lvl 45, double and triple hit for 100 plus.
